  <brief_title>Topical vs Oral Metronidazole After Benign Anorectal Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Topical Versus Oral Metronidazole for Pain Relief After Surgery for Benign Anorectal Conditions; a Prospective Randomized Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
